Báb Patricia Baillie (&#1575;&#1604;&#1576;&#1575;&#1576; Patricia Baillie) is the founder of Plasticfarianism and the arbiter of all disputes.

Disagreement with Báb Patricia on any religious matter constitutes the creation of a schism.

Disagreement with Báb Patricia on the question of which matters are religious constitutes the creation of a schism.